function.description:
Sets a single cookie. Cookies must be specified as a list in the format:
{ name: name, //eg. "Xillio_cookie" path: path, //eg. "/" domain: domain, //eg. ".xillio.com", value:value, //eg. "Delivery finished." expires: expiry date //eg. "2012-10-18T09:42:15" }
The name attribute is mandatory, the others are optional. Current cookie information can be obtained through Web.pageInfo. Cookies can be removed using Web.removeCookie. Due to the nature of Xill IDE, all cookies will be removed every time Xill IDE is restarted.

example.code:
use Web;
use System;

var page = Web.loadPage("http://www.xillio.com");
Web.removeAllCookies(page);
var cookie = {"name":"Xillio", "path":"/", "domain":"www.xillio.com", "value":"123", "expires":"2018-10-18T09:42:15"};
Web.setCookie(page, cookie);
System.print(Web.pageInfo(page));
Web.removeCookie(page, "Xillio");
System.print(Web.pageInfo(page));
